{
  "stem": "1677.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Forget the English, because we will come under the Russian interest zone here in Czechoslovakia as the war is going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, I want a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], a Jewish commander, a commander.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They found one, a major, spoke Yiddish, to my bad luck, from Kiev.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His whole family was murdered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said to me, I do everything for you if you give me, as a souvenir, your number.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can I take this as a souvenir from you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, have it, by all means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- I'm very hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have a sister and three other girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are five together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are-- we want to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will help you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I bring you food first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came back in 10 minutes and brought a huge, big cake, a huge cake of gouda cheese, which I not only couldn't hold-- because it was too heavy for me-- not a knife to cut it, no-- neither strength to do it.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is the story of my life, that the first food which was offered to me, I couldn't accept because I couldn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was very wise that I didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the girls in the camps who stayed there-- and I believe it was very dirty there after-- they, to, as a victory celebration, they roasted an ox, which they requisitioned, on a spear.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were sitting there waiting, the stupid women who didn't eat for years, and ate this half-cooked flesh and had busted stomach walls.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And more died after the eighth of May than before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then it all went very quick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One could catch a train with great difficulties.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came to a first class compartment, because there was no room anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
